name: Waroeng Munduk Luwih
address: M5M7+277, Br.Munduk andong, Bangli, Kec. Baturiti, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82191, Indonesia
review 1: Upon arrival, we sat down and a nest of bees buzzed above us and stung us.  After this incident we moved to the tables.  we ordered fried noodles and fried rice with the condition that the food would not be spicy.  After being brought, these foods could not be eaten at all as they were hot.  The attendant only said sorry and gave us the full amount to pay.  Almost 100 rp wasted unnecessarily
review 2: Nice place. Fantastic views. Good Indonesian food at very reasonable prices
review 3: The best food I have ever eaten in Bali!!!
review 4: Nice place....very interesting, environment very natural n relax
review 5: Food were ok,  just wanted to support this local venue
